==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌkʃən|-ʌkʃən]]

===Noun===
'''reduction'''
#The act, process, or result of [[reducing]]
#The [[amount]] by which something is [[reduced]]
#* A 5% '''reduction''' in robberies
#{{chemistry}} A [[reaction]] in which [[electron]]s are [[gain]]ed and [[valence]] is reduced; often by the [[removal]] of [[oxygen]] or the [[addition]] of [[hydrogen]]
#(''cooking'') The process of [[rapidly]] [[boiling]] a [[sauce]] to [[concentrate]] it
===Antonyms===
*[[increase]]
*[[oxidation]]

